room_title: Escape room "Meltdown" by Escape the Room Chicago in Chicago
review: This is an amazing bonding experience - if you come in, you are not going to regret it. Make every minute count and get into full mode right away, as one hour flies by. We almost made it with two clues left.

room_title: Escape room "Meltdown" by Escape the Room Chicago in Chicago
review: Great place to have lots of fun and laughs with friends and family. Definelty recommend!

room_title: Escape room "Meltdown" by Escape the Room Chicago in Chicago
review: An unbelievable experience! The staff did a great job of walking us through the process. Our group had an amazing time and a lot of fun. I highly recommend this to anyone looking for a fun, challenging night out!
